    "The usage and settings of automatic metrics vary across papers and even within a paper.",
    "For example, variations",
    "Page 19 of 30 18 include the number of top words, the number of topics, reference corpora, and coherence or diversity metrics.",
    "Consequently, the results are often confined to specific studies, impeding the comparability of NTMs across different research papers.",
